{"tid":2455813,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"7年連降創歷史新低！2020年 支國結婚登記同比下降12.2％","createTime":"2021-03-21T11:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T09:19:55.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4df8dc0883c25e08024074054e6a72df2da96946","tid":2455813,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T11:53:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1cUa1Na.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1cUa1Na.jpg&h=68fc52d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者對比近年來的婚姻登記數據發現，結婚登記人數從2013年後呈現持續下降的趨勢，2020年全國結婚登記人數再創新低。<br />\n<br />\n近日，2020年民政統計數據出爐，全國結婚登記人數813.1萬對，同比下降12.2%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://user.guancha.cn/main/content?id=477178&amp;s=fwzxhfbt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fuser.guancha.cn%2Fmain%2Fcontent%3Fid%3D477178%26s%3Dfwzxhfbt&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfUPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=5663a54d\" target=\"_blank\">https://user.guancha.cn/main/content?id=477178&amp;s=fwzxhfbt</a>"},{"pid":"2ae1d8b343a48a6c0cdcf0621b004e2ad68ab2c3","tid":2455813,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T11:55:18.000Z","msg":"2020全國結婚數據分析<br />\n結婚登記人數持續下降受多種影響<br />\n結婚登記人數持續下降，是受到多種因素影響的。<br />\n首先，是因為新冠疫情影響，全國多地婚姻登記處長時間關閉。<br />\n其次，適婚人群數量的減少。根據第一財經的報道，結婚對數是與出生人口相對應的，創下近十年最高峰的2013年，對應的恰好是1987年的出生人口高峰。<br />\n按照趨勢，未來幾年結婚對數還將繼續走低&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n分省數據<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_11405955\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.thepaper.cn%2FnewsDetail_forward_11405955&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfUPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=6a2740b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_11405955</a>"},{"pid":"feaa24773c56923ad451c094d6ba542a55bee1b0","tid":2455813,"uid":155095,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T11:56:33.000Z","msg":"黨會逼你結婚同交配 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br 